#

Creamy Yogurt Guacamole

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackHealthy

Description

A rich and creamy twist on traditional guacamole, perfect as a dip or spread!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • plain greek yogurt: 1/2 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
  • chopped cilantro: 2 tablespoons
  • diced tomatoes: 1/2 cup
  • diced onion: 1/4 cup
